              "kind": "plain",
              "text": "4381 - "
            },
            {
              "kind": "plain",
              "text": "رَوَى مُحَمَّدُ بْنُ اَلْوَلِيدِ"
            },
            {
              "kind": "plain",
              "text": " عَنِ "
            },
            {
              "kind": "narrator",
              "path": "/people/narrators/764",
              "text": "اَلْحُسَيْنِ بْنِ بَشَّارٍ"
            },
            {
              "kind": "plain",
              "text": " قَالَ"
            }
          ]
        },
        "part_type": "Hadith",
        "path": "/books/man-la-yahduruhu-al-faqih:3:3:15:1",
        "source_url": "https://thaqalayn.net/hadith/34/3/15/1",
        "text": [
          ": كَتَبْتُ إِلَى أَبِي جَعْفَرٍ عَلَيْهِ اَلسَّلاَمُ فِي رَجُلٍ خَطَبَ إِلَيَّ فَكَتَبَ \"مَنْ خَطَبَ إِلَيْكُمْ فَرَضِيتُمْ دِينَهُ وَ أَمَانَتَهُ كَائِناً مَنْ كَانَ فَزَوِّجُوهُ وَ إِلاَّ تَفْعَلُوا \"تَكُنْ فِتْنَةٌ فِي اَلْأَرْضِ وَ فَسٰادٌ كَبِيرٌ\" \"."
        ],
        "translations": {
          "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
            "Hadith.4381 - Muhammad ibn al-Walid narrated from al-Husayn ibn Bashshar, who said:\nI wrote to Abu Ja'far Imam Muhammad ibn Ali Al-Baqir (as) concerning a man who proposed marriage to someone.\nImam (as) replied: \"If someone proposes to you, and you are satisfied with his religion and trustworthiness, then marry him, whoever he may be. If you do not do so, there will be 'fitnah (discord) on the earth and great corruption.'\""
          ]
        }
      },
      {
        "index": 2865,
        "local_index": 2,
        "narrator_chain": {
          "parts": [
            {
              "kind": "plain",
              "text": "4382 - "
            },
            {
              "kind": "narrator",
              "path": "/people/narrators/213",
              "text": "و"
            },
            {
              "kind": "plain",
              "text": "َ قَالَ"
            }
          ]
        },
        "part_type": "Hadith",
        "path": "/books/man-la-yahduruhu-al-faqih:3:3:15:2",
        "source_url": "https://thaqalayn.net/hadith/34/3/15/2",
        "text": [
          " رَسُولُ اَللَّهِ صَلَّى اَللَّهُ عَلَيْهِ وَ آلِهِ : \" \"إِنَّمٰا أَنَا بَشَرٌ مِثْلُكُمْ\" أَتَزَوَّجُ فِيكُمْ وَ أُزَوِّجُكُمْ إِلاَّ فَاطِمَةَ فَإِنَّ تَزْوِيجَهَا نَزَلَ مِنَ اَلسَّمَاءِ \"."
        ],
        "translations": {
          "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
            "Hadith.4382 - The Messenger of Allah (swt) (peace be upon him and his family) said:\n\"I am only a human being like you; I marry amongst you and I arrange marriages for you.\nExcept for Sayyida Fatimah {s.a}, for her marriage was decreed from the heavens.\""
          ]
        }
      },
      {
        "index": 2866,
        "local_index": 3,
        "narrator_chain": {
          "parts": [
            {
              "kind": "plain",
              "text": "4383 - "
            },
            {
              "kind": "narrator",
              "path": "/people/narrators/213",
              "text": "و"
            },
            {
              "kind": "plain",
              "text": "َ قَالَ"
            }
          ]
        },
        "part_type": "Hadith",
        "path": "/books/man-la-yahduruhu-al-faqih:3:3:15:3",
        "source_url": "https://thaqalayn.net/hadith/34/3/15/3",
        "text": [
          " عَلَيْهِ اَلسَّلاَمُ: \"لَوْ لاَ أَنَّ اَللَّهَ تَعَالَى خَلَقَ فَاطِمَةَ لِعَلِيٍّ مَا كَانَ لَهَا عَلَى وَجْهِ اَلْأَرْضِ كُفْوٌ آدَمُ فَمَنْ دُونَهُ\"."
        ],
        "translations": {
          "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
            "Hadith.4383 - Imam (as) said: \"Had Allah (swt), the Exalted, not created Sayyida Fatimah {s.a} for Imam Ali ibn Abi Talib (as), there would not have been any equal for her on the face of the earth, from Adam to those after him.\""
          ]
        }
      },
      {
        "index": 2867,
        "local_index": 4,
        "narrator_chain": {
